"Abstract In my July column, I mentioned the forthcoming review of the 1992 Guidelines for the Security of Information Systems, which had recently begun within the Paris-based Organization for Economic Cooperation and Development (OECD/OCDE). The Guidelines were formally adopted by the Council of the OECD as a Recommendation at its 793rd Session on 26–27 November 1992 (ref. C(92)188/FINAL)."
